data.description:
Invest in Prime Development Property! Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to develop 40 acres within the city limits of Hastings, Michigan.  Corner piece with city utilities available at the street.  Rolling hills bordered by beautiful woods and a small pond.  Density and demographic information regarding the needs for housing in Barry county is available.  
Also included is a farmhouse with a barn on the property that could be used or parceled off for future use.  House and property are sold together.
